videos.headline: Memphis' Ellis banks in half-court shot at the buzzer
videos.description: With time running out in the first half, Memphis' Boogie Ellis comes up with a steal and banks in a half-court shot at the buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Memphis' Ellis banks in half-court shot at the buzzer) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Memphis looks rusty with early wardrobe malfunction
videos.description: After Saint Mary's got out to an 8-0 lead, Memphis' D.J. Jeffries checks into the game but mistakenly has his jersey on backwards.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Memphis looks rusty with early wardrobe malfunction) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Memphis' Cisse slams home alley-oop over defender
videos.description: Boogie Ellis lobs it to Moussa Cisse, who slams down the alley-oop over a defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Memphis’ Cisse slams home alley-oop over defender) 2020/11/25 ESHEET
